Alphapose Installation:

1- Install some dependencies for some required packages:

sudo apt-get install python3 python3-dev python3-pip libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev zlib1g-dev libffi-dev libssl-dev

2- Install required packages:

pip3 install Scrapy

pip3 install ninja

pip3 install -U PyYAML

pip install Cython

sudo apt-get install libyaml-dev

3- cd where you would like to clone the project.

git clone https://github.com/MVIG-SJTU/AlphaPose

4- cd to AlphaPose folder and run setup.py

python3 setup.py build develop


